title: [Hollowlair, Dreadgrounds]
description: /mrt day;With every step, flames gutter and roil from crevices in the ground, which spew not only fire but also stifling plumes of noxious fumes and smoke.  Visibility waxes and wanes in these cavernous depths, making every footfall a risk and every breath potentially the last.
